{"word":"Ishmael","slug":"ishmael","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ishmael</b> <a href=\"#/H3458\">H3458</a> <br/> 1. Son of Abraham:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=16&verse=11'>Gen 16:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=16&verse=16'>Gen 16:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=1&verse=28'>1Ch 1:28</a> <br/> - Prayer of Abraham for<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=17&verse=18'>Gen 17:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=17&verse=20'>Gen 17:20</a> <br/> - Circumcised<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=17&verse=26'>Gen 17:26</a> <br/> - Promised to be the father of a nation<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=16&verse=12'>Gen 16:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=17&verse=20'>Gen 17:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=13'>Gen 21:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=18'>Gen 21:18</a> <br/> - Sent away by Abraham<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=21'>Gen 21:21</a> <br/> - With Isaac buries his father<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=9'>Gen 25:9</a> <br/> - Children of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=18'>Gen 25:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=1&verse=31'>1Ch 1:31</a> <br/> - Daughter of, marries Esau<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=28&verse=9'>Gen 28:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=3'>Gen 36:3</a> <br/> - Death of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=18'>Gen 25:18</a> <br/> 2. Father of Zebadiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=19&verse=11'>2Ch 19:11</a><br/> 3. A son of Azel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=8&verse=38'>1Ch 8:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=44'>1Ch 9:44</a><br/> 4. One of the captains of hundreds<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=23&verse=1'>2Ch 23:1</a><br/> 5. A priest of the exile<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=10&verse=22'>Ezr 10:22</a><br/> 6. A son of Nethaniah:<br/> - Assassinated Gedaliah, governor of Judah under king of Babylon, and takes captive many Jews<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=40&verse=16'>Jer 40:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=41&verse=11'>Jer 41:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=25&verse=25'>2Ki 25:25</a> <br/> - Defeated by Johanan, and put to flight<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=41&verse=15'>Jer 41:15</a> "}]}